Package: aurion-desktop-environment
Architecture: all
Depends:
 aurion-shell,
 aurion-settings,
 aurion-files,
 aurion-notifications,
 aurion-session,
 aurion-sddm-theme,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: AurionOS desktop environment alpha meta package
 Native AurionOS desktop-environment layer for the alpha ISO.

Package: aurion-shell
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pyqt5, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AurionOS shell alpha components
 Native topbar, dock, launcher, and desktop hub.

Package: aurion-settings
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pyqt5, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AurionOS settings alpha
 Settings and control-center surfaces.

Package: aurion-files
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pyqt5, xdg-utils, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AurionOS file manager alpha
 Lightweight native file manager surface with PCManFM fallback.

Package: aurion-notifications
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pyqt5, libnotify-bin, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AurionOS notification center alpha
 Native notification center and notifier bridge.

Package: aurion-session
Architecture: all
Depends: openbox | labwc, pcmanfm-qt, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AurionOS session alpha
 Native preview session and window-manager bridge.

Package: aurion-sddm-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: sddm, qml-module-qtquick-controls2, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AurionOS SDDM theme alpha
 Login screen theme assets for AurionOS.
